Alias MyB0 B0
Alias Myanti-B0 anti-B0
ChargeConj MyB0 Myanti-B0
Alias MyD*- D*-
Alias MyD*+ D*+
ChargeConj MyD*- MyD*+

Alias MyD0 D0
Alias Myanti-D0 anti-D0
ChargeConj MyD0 Myanti-D0



Decay Upsilon(4S)
# without mixing
0.5 MyB0 anti-B0       VSS;
0.5 Myanti-B0 B0       VSS;
Enddecay

# Decay of B0 -> D*- pi+
Decay MyB0
1.0 rho+ D*-		SVV_HELAMP  0.317 0.19 0.936 0.0 0.152 1.47; 
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-B0

Decay MyD*+
1.0 MyD0 pi+            VSS;
Enddecay

Decay MyD*-
1.0 Myanti-D0 pi-       VSS;
Enddecay

Decay MyD0
1.0 K- pi+              PHSP;
Enddecay

Decay Myanti-D0
1.0 K+ pi-              PHSP;
Enddecay

End

